title: Max Keiser - On The Edge 2012 May 25 FR [sebaygo1]

On The Edge (Press TV)
- with Max Keiser -
Friday, 25 April 2012


[sebaygo1]


In this edition of On the Edge, Max interviews Karl Denninger from market-ticker.org. He talks about the finical crisis in Greece and how it will unfold in near future. Karl Denninger was the CEO of MCSNet in Chicago, one of the area's first Internet providers. He is a founding contributor to conservative blog market-ticker.org and was one of the early members of the Tea Party movement.
      


The .mp3 in the torrent is extracted audio from the Press TV video. You can watch the video here: http://www.presstv.com/Program/243166.html
